acts on the boundary conditions as $A\to B\to C\to A,AB\to BC\to AC\to
AB$, the boundary conditions $F$ and $N$ are fixed. We shall only write
out flows modulo this symmetry, e.g.\ the flow $A\oplus
B\longrightarrow AB$ stands also for $B\oplus C\longrightarrow BC$ and
$C\oplus A\to AC$.

\begin{itemize}
